        "response": {
          "bodySize": 1408,
          "content": {
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1408,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01DYBwYbjk11hDk6wTW918cy\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"I've suggested a few keywords your audience is likely searching for when your ad appears.\\n\\nHow do these sound to you?\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"keywords\\\": [\\n    \\\"meeting scheduling tool for remote teams\\\",\\n    \\\"automatic calendar coordination software\\\",\\n    \\\"find meeting time across time zones\\\",\\n    \\\"team scheduling software\\\",\\n    \\\"meeting scheduler for distributed teams\\\",\\n    \\\"calendar sync for global teams\\\",\\n    \\\"best scheduling tool for remote work\\\",\\n    \\\"eliminate meeting coordination emails\\\"\\n  ]\\n}\\n```\\n\\nThese keywords target:\\n- **High-intent transactional** (keywords 1, 4, 5, 7): People actively searching for scheduling solutions\\n- **Problem-focused** (keywords 3, 8): Teams frustrated with current coordination methods\\n- **Time zone specific** (keywords 2, 6): Directly addresses your core value proposition\\n- **Awareness/comparison** (keyword 7): Captures teams evaluating options\\n\\nReady to move forward with these, or would you like me to adjust the focus?\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":992,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":232,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
