            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1287,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_013LDNYHSCeCHfaHwugVSbCS\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"I've suggested a few keywords your audience is likely searching for when your ad appears.\\n\\nHow do these sound to you?\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"keywords\\\": [\\n    \\\"meeting scheduling software\\\",\\n    \\\"timezone meeting scheduler\\\",\\n    \\\"find meeting time across timezones\\\",\\n    \\\"calendar coordination tool\\\",\\n    \\\"remote team scheduling\\\",\\n    \\\"automatic meeting scheduler\\\",\\n    \\\"distributed team meeting planner\\\",\\n    \\\"schedule meetings across time zones\\\"\\n  ]\\n}\\n```\\n\\nThese keywords target:\\n- **High-intent transactional** (keywords 1, 3, 6, 8): People actively searching for scheduling solutions\\n- **Problem-focused** (keywords 4, 5, 7): Teams struggling with coordination and distribution\\n- **Solution-specific** (keywords 2): Direct timezone-related searches your tool solves\\n\\nReady to move forward with these, or would you like me to adjust any of them?\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":1742,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":209,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
