            <example_response>\\n\\n        Here are some fresh suggestions:\\n\\n        ```json\\n        {\\n  \\\"callouts\\\": [\\n    \\\"Feature 1\\\",\\n    \\\"Feature 2\\\",\\n    \\\"Feature 3\\\"\\n  ]\\n}\\n        ```\\n\\n            </example_response>\"}]}"
