            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01LJPPyDQ72754F5U7ABbc4c\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Next, let's spell out some unique features of your business.\\n\\nThis helps your ad take up more real estate, and gives your users more reasons to click. I filled in a few ideas to help get us started.\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"callouts\\\": [\\n    \\\"80% Less Scheduling\\\",\\n    \\\"Works Across Time Zones\\\",\\n    \\\"2,000+ Teams Trust Us\\\",\\n    \\\"Instant Meeting Times\\\",\\n    \\\"Free Demo Available\\\",\\n    \\\"No Credit Card Needed\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"structuredSnippets\\\": {\\n    \\\"category\\\": \\\"services\\\",\\n    \\\"details\\\": [\\n      \\\"Calendar Integration\\\",\\n      \\\"Time Zone Matching\\\",\\n      \\\"Team Availability Sync\\\"\\n    ]\\n  }\\n}\\n```\\n\\nThese callouts highlight your biggest competitive advantages—the time savings, social proof, and ease of getting started. The structured snippets show exactly what your scheduling tool does.\\n\\nFeel free to swap any of these out or let me know if you'd like me to adjust the tone or focus!\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":1801,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":234,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
