            "size": 1734,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01LC1hEUG9KUNR53zTYTu7SX\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"I've suggested a few keywords your audience is likely searching for when your ad appears.\\n\\nHow do these sound to you?\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"keywords\\\": [\\n    \\\"meeting scheduler for remote teams\\\",\\n    \\\"find meeting time across time zones\\\",\\n    \\\"calendar scheduling tool\\\",\\n    \\\"team meeting coordinator\\\",\\n    \\\"automated meeting scheduling\\\",\\n    \\\"best scheduling software for distributed teams\\\",\\n    \\\"meeting time finder\\\",\\n    \\\"schedule meetings across continents\\\"\\n  ]\\n}\\n```\\n\\nThese keywords target:\\n- **High-intent transactional keywords** (people ready to solve their scheduling problem): \\\"meeting scheduler for remote teams,\\\" \\\"calendar scheduling tool,\\\" \\\"automated meeting scheduling\\\"\\n- **Problem-focused keywords** (people searching for solutions): \\\"find meeting time across time zones,\\\" \\\"schedule meetings across continents\\\"\\n- **Awareness keywords** (broader searches): \\\"team meeting coordinator,\\\" \\\"best scheduling software for distributed teams,\\\" \\\"meeting time finder\\\"\\n\\nAll of these align with your target audience of remote teams and project managers frustrated with scheduling chaos. When someone searches these terms, your ad will show up right when they need it most.\\n\\nWhat do you think? Want to adjust any of these or add keywords for specific industries or use cases?\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":1868,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":272,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
