          "url": "https://api.anthropic.com/v1/messages"
        },
        "response": {
          "bodySize": 1299,
          "content": {
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1299,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_014v76Ng9mXZ7eYvpVqEZ2Zt\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Next, let's spell out some unique features of your business.\\n\\nThis helps your ad take up more real estate, and gives your users more reasons to click. I filled in a few ideas to help get us started.\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"callouts\\\": [\\n    \\\"80% Less Time\\\",\\n    \\\"Works Across Zones\\\",\\n    \\\"One-Click Scheduling\\\",\\n    \\\"2,000+ Teams Trust Us\\\",\\n    \\\"Free Demo Available\\\",\\n    \\\"No Credit Card Needed\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"structuredSnippets\\\": {\\n    \\\"category\\\": \\\"services\\\",\\n    \\\"details\\\": [\\n      \\\"Calendar Integration\\\",\\n      \\\"Time Zone Matching\\\",\\n      \\\"Team Availability Sync\\\"\\n    ]\\n  }\\n}\\n```\\n\\nThese callouts highlight your biggest competitive advantages—the time savings, global reach, and social proof that matter most to distributed teams. The structured snippets spell out exactly what your tool does, so prospects know immediately if it solves their problem.\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":1619,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":223,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
