        "response": {
          "bodySize": 1399,
          "content": {
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1399,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_016BCug6rDyQa6a418TQgN12\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"I've suggested a few keywords your audience is likely searching for when your ad appears.\\n\\nHow do these sound to you?\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"keywords\\\": [\\n    \\\"meeting scheduler for remote teams\\\",\\n    \\\"find meeting time across time zones\\\",\\n    \\\"calendar coordination tool\\\",\\n    \\\"automated meeting scheduling software\\\",\\n    \\\"best scheduling tool for distributed teams\\\",\\n    \\\"meeting scheduler near me\\\",\\n    \\\"how to schedule meetings across time zones\\\",\\n    \\\"team calendar management software\\\"\\n  ]\\n}\\n```\\n\\nThese keywords target the exact pain points your customers are searching for—from the practical problem (\\\"find meeting time across time zones\\\") to the solution they're looking for (\\\"meeting scheduler for remote teams\\\"). They mix high-intent transactional keywords with broader awareness keywords so your ads show up whether someone's actively shopping or just researching options.\\n\\nWant to adjust any of these, or should we move forward to testing them?\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":1690,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":203,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
